  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2733951/" class="title-link">总算没白花钱</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2733951"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/2733685/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2733685-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2733685/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">黄章晋</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-11-10"
      class="main-meta">2009-11-10 14:06:29</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2733951_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  一口气从网上订购了300多块钱关于古代军事的书，结果只有这一本是靠谱的，其他几本不是满嘴跑火车就是陈词滥调，还有一本讲中国古兵器的，那就更是明目张胆的抢钱了，里面就是一些私人藏品的图鉴，基本无任何参考价值。

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/2733951/#comments">(5回应)</a>
