  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="3106372">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3106372/" class="title-link">和刘永华的《中国古代军戎服饰》配合着读</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3106372"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1174955/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1174955-52.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1174955/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">戏作三昧</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-03-19"
      class="main-meta">2010-03-19 11:13:18</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3106372_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  刘永华的书是精美手绘，真人复原。陈大威这本是电脑绘画，资料工具。手绘更直观更精致，而且刘永华书中有大量实物出土的原型考证说明。相比较，陈大威这本和国内出的军服系列是一类的，目的在于“工具”说明，而非艺术享受。 工具好处是内容丰富，缺陷是色彩人物材质没有真实感...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/3106372/#comments">(4回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">8有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_3106372_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_3106372_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










